data.description: This fully remodeled 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home offers an inviting open floor plan with a 2 carport and long driveway. This home has many great features including Impact doors and windows, newer AC and water heater, remodeled bathroom, flooring, and paint, with a nice fenced in backyard! The property also features its own private washroom attached with a washer and dryerThis single family home has No HOA, perfect for a first time home buyer or investor.
